Package entrants.utils.graph

Class Node

  • java.lang.Object
    • entrants.utils.graph.Node
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    NodeInterface, java.lang.Comparable
    public class Node
extends java.lang.Object
implements NodeInterface
    This class represents a node on the PacMan game A Node is a point in the 2D world, it can contain & pill, a power pill, a pacman, some ghosts. Each Node in the world is identified by an index.
